                            "default_value": "<h3>Upcoming Events<\/h3>\r\nSee Upcoming Brand Partner events on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/groups\/radicalbrandpartners\/events\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Facebook Group events page here.<\/a>\r\n\r\nHere is a list of some upcoming events for planning purposes.  <strong>These will be hosted on Zoom at 10:00am PST \/ 1:00pm EST<\/strong>.  For a recording of past events, please scroll down.\r\n\r\n<strong>MAY<\/strong>\r\n\r\n<em>3rd       Coffee + Conversation <strong>(Brand Partners Only)<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/geA4yjiNSok\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Zoom Recording)<\/a><\/em>\r\n\r\n<em>5th       Product Focus + Promotions <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/6FPSGsRDXjw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Zoom Recording)<\/a><\/em>\r\n\r\n<em>10th     Radical SPF Training <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/f6cC9LlRKN0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Zoom Link)<\/a><\/em>\r\n\r\n<em>12th     Radical Start Brand Partner Training <strong>(Taught by Marijane Relth)<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/cmJJ3ppPvVc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Zoom Recording)<\/a><\/em>\r\n\r\n17th     Cocktails + Conversation <strong>(Brand Partners +<\/strong> <strong>Guests)<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.eventbrite.com\/e\/153667618985\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Registration Link)<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/zoom.us\/j\/98851844372\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Zoom Link)<\/a>\r\n\r\n19th     Radical Start Training <strong>(Taught by Nancy Murphy) <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/zoom.us\/j\/97257900090\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Zoom Link)<\/a>\r\n\r\n20th.    Product Launch Event - Rejuvafirm CBD Resurfacing Serum <strong>(5 PM Pacific Time)<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/zoom.us\/j\/98341773075\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Zoom Link)<\/a>\r\n\r\n24th     <strong>Radical Deep Dive:<\/strong> Get Radical: Secrets to Creating a Life You Love – Chapter 3 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.eventbrite.com\/e\/153679709147\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Registration Link)<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/zoom.us\/j\/91852608940\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Zoom Link)<\/a>\r\n\r\n26th     Radical Start Training <strong>(Taught by Emily Chapman) <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/zoom.us\/j\/97257900090\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(Zoom Link)<\/a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>PLAN AHEAD:  MONTHLY MONDAY SCHEDULE <\/strong>\r\n\r\n1st Monday – Coffee + Conversation (10am PST \/ 12pm CST \/ 1pm EST) - <em><strong>Brand Partners Only<\/strong><\/em>\r\n\r\n2nd Monday – Product + Promotions Training (10am PST \/ 12pm CST \/ 1pm EST)\r\n\r\n3rd Monday – Cocktails + Conversation (5pm PST \/ 7pm CST \/ 8pm EST)\r\n\r\n4th Monday – Radical Deep Dive (10am PST \/ 12pm CST \/ 1pm EST)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Past Events<\/h3>\r\n<strong>Topic: Radical Start Brand Partner Training (by Marijane Relth)\r\nDate: May 12, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/cmJJ3ppPvVc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Radical SPF Training\r\nDate: May 10, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/f6cC9LlRKN0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Product Focus + Promotions\r\nDate: May 5, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/6FPSGsRDXjw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Get Radical: Coffee + Conversation (Brand Partners Only)\r\nDate: May 3, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/geA4yjiNSok\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Get Radical: Secrets to Creating a Life You Love – Chapter 2\r\nDate: April 28, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/jk6JJXVUHBE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Best Practices from Leading Brand Partners\r\nDate: April 21, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/qAf8Y7xH3y4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Cocktails + Conversation\r\nDate: April 19, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/W4_qt561KTM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Radical Product Kits + Enrollment Collections<\/strong>\r\n<strong>Date: April 14, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/b7SvESxaCyU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n<a href=\"https:\/\/radicalskincare.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/Radical-Product-Kits-Enrollment-Collections.pdf\">Radical Product Kits &amp; Enrollment Collections<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Build a Radical Team\r\nDate: April 7, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=puig4EPvwFo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Coffee + Conversation (Brand Partners Only)\r\nDate: April 5, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/fC5zpA9Oq2A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n<a href=\"https:\/\/radicalskincare.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/Radical-Coffee-and-Conversation.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Radical Coffee and Conversation PDF<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Get Radical: Secrets to Creating a Life You Love - Chapter 1\r\nDate: March 31, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/FfL2mGV3tao\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: A Walk Through Your Back Office\r\nDate: March 25, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/5AgO8-QezG8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Topic: Using Radical Skincare Creative Resources\r\nDate: March 17, 2021\r\n<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/cVQmzw2rTnE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zoom Call Recording<\/a>\r\n<a href=\"https:\/\/radicalskincare.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03